# Track Map

Track Map is an application for tracking people groups in a map. These are some of the options that will be available:

  - Create a map and invite people to join to.
  - Join to a map
  - View people info: distance, name, avatar...

#### and more features coming soon!

  - Login
  - Quick join with QR

Last version available

```sh
Last Version 1.0.0
```

#### Google Play App

See [Google Play App](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.handysparksoft.trackmap)
